data.description: Welcome to 1687 Rolling View Way, a charming retreat nestled in the peaceful neighborhood of Harbins Landing Estates. This lovely home features 4 bedrooms & 2.5 bathrooms of comfortable living space. As you step inside, you are greeted by a bright and airy interior, with a two story foyer. The open floor plan is perfect for everyday living and entertaining. The spacious living room is bathed in natural light and a stone fireplace creating a bright and welcoming atmosphere. The kitchen is a chef's dream, with double ovens, gas cooktop, granite countertops, ample cabinet space making meal preparation a breeze. Enjoy casual meals in the cozy breakfast nook or host dinner parties in the elegant dining room. The upper level of the home hosts the owners suite which is a private oasis, offering a peaceful retreat at the end of the day. The ensuite bathroom features double vanity, walk-in closet, a soaking tub, and a separate shower perfect for unwinding and relaxing. Outside, the landscaped yard offers a private oasis, featuring a covered patio and fenced in yard perfect for enjoying the outdoors year-round. Located in a prime location with schools, parks, shopping, dining, and entertainment options just moments away, this home offers the perfect blend of luxury and convenience. Don't miss your chance to own this wonderful home. Schedule your showing today!
